{"word":"G2168 - εὐχαριστέω - eucharistéō - yoo-khar-is-teh'-o - Thank","slug":"G2168","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐχαριστέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>eucharistéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yoo-khar-is-teh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Thank"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x03C5;&#x0313;&#x03C7;&#x03B1;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - eucharisteo&#x0304;</b> - <i>yoo-khar-is-teh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G2170\">G2170</a>; to <i>be grateful</i>, that is, (actually) to <i>express gratitude</i> (towards); specifically to <i>say grace</i> at a meal: - (give) thank (-ful, -s)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2169\">G2169</a>, <a href=\"#/G2170\">G2170</a>, <a href=\"#/G4796\">G4796</a>, <a href=\"#/G5463\">G5463</a>, <a href=\"#/G5479\">G5479</a>, <a href=\"#/G5483\">G5483</a>, <a href=\"#/G5484\">G5484</a>, <a href=\"#/G5485\">G5485</a>, <a href=\"#/G5486\">G5486</a>, <a href=\"#/G5487\">G5487</a>, <a href=\"#/G884\">G884</a>"}]}